org.ggp.base.util.propnet.factory.converter

Class PropNetConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ggp.base.util.propnet.factory.converter.PropNetConverter

  • public final class PropNetConverter
extends java.lang.Object
    The PropNetConverter class defines PropNet conversion for the PropNetFactory class. This takes in a flattened game description, and converts it into an equivalent PropNet.

    • Method Detail

      • convert

        public PropNet convert(java.util.List<Role> roles,
              java.util.List<GdlRule> description)
        Converts a game description to a PropNet using the following process (note that this method and all of the methods that it invokes assume that description has already been flattened by a PropNetFlattener):
        1. Transforms each of the rules in description into equivalent PropNet Components.
        2. Adds or gates to Propositions with more than one input.
        3. Adds inputs that are implicitly specified by description.
        Parameters:
        description - A game description.
        Returns:
        An equivalent PropNet.
